{"tid":2442008,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"歷史博物館去殖 港督牆消失","createTime":"2021-03-11T05:42:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T06:09:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a539d4309551bd2e1b12283b358e2335abea48aa","tid":2442008,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T05:42:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210311/RPIGSS76U5GVZFQVXWDG2T6BMM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210311%2FRPIGSS76U5GVZFQVXWDG2T6BMM%2F&d=XsjoyflP4JPXBkuZaWCkHRmaKe8vvTAxx9uYoYxOzRs%3D&h=3f86d7fe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210311%2FRPIGSS76U5GVZFQVXWDG2T6BMM%2F&h=95964805\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210311/RPIGSS76U5GVZFQVXWDG2T6BMM/</a><br />\n<br />\n歷史博物館去殖 港督牆消失<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】中共支配下，香港特色新歷史正式誕生。香港歷史博物館開放19年的「香港故事」常設展覽，去年底閉館翻新兩年，翻新期間以「經典再現&mdash;&mdash;香港故事精華展」代替。精華展內容對「殖民地」隻字不提，港英旗幟及港督照片亦被消失 ，討論一國兩制的篇幅有所增加。<br />\n<br />\n「經典再現&mdash;&mdash;香港故事精華展」去。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/-oeTAXlJvnmhVKaYiB0NaB_FIcA=/1364x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BA4LTA6LQFHG5H3S33VZSKA6PI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F-oeTAXlJvnmhVKaYiB0NaB_FIcA%3D%2F1364x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBA4LTA6LQFHG5H3S33VZSKA6PI.jpg&h=c0e3c2b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■翻新前的展館對殖民地時期着墨頗多，設有歷代港督牆，介紹其貢獻。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一國兩制篇幅增加<br />\n<br />\n以往常設展中的「香港回歸」展區對香港殖民地歷史着墨不少，說明香港經歷百多年的殖民地統治。原有展區中展示戰後歷任總督的政績和政治制度，以「殖民地時期的政治體制」展板為例，文中首句已是「在1997年6月30日前，香港是英國的殖民地，而港督是英皇授權統治香港的全權代表」。以往的常設展更有兩面牆展示一排歷代港督肖像及貢獻，成為港人打卡熱點，惟現時所有港督照片一張不留。<br />\n<br />\n惟現有的精華展中，「香港回歸」展板對殖民時期和身份一概不提，探討「一國兩制」的篇幅則有所增加，包括指出鄧小平提出一國兩制的初步構想，強調一國兩制的重要性。<br />\n<br />\n「香港回歸」的英文標題字眼亦有所不同。以往「香港回歸」繙譯為「Return of Hong Kong 1997（1997年香港回歸）」，新展板標題卻改成「Return to the Motherland（回歸祖國）」。<br />\n<br />\n廖先生與女友一同前來看展覽，認為精華展「cut（刪除）咗好多細節嘢，你feel（感覺）到係揀咗某啲嘢嚟講」。他續指「講好多嗰啲雜貨種類，我自己覺得有啲無聊&hellip;&hellip;政治方面講少咗好多」，直指展覽的「觀賞指數低咗好多」。<br />\n<br />\n康文署回覆指，精華展因。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/6CaPf8SbTTfJWe2zsSxnlSsP7d4=/989x569/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4ZJPRHGOMJGUJMR7NKCARKK7HQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F6CaPf8SbTTfJWe2zsSxnlSsP7d4%3D%2F989x569%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4ZJPRHGOMJGUJMR7NKCARKK7HQ.jpg&h=7d8944fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■展中英文標題「Return of Hong Kong 1997」改為「Return to the Motherland」（紅框示）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/eynMc3hU4y-alsrU8WwFW9mJQYU=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MRAWEGWWSRG2JMAKWMXQATPR2M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FeynMc3hU4y-alsrU8WwFW9mJQYU%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMRAWEGWWSRG2JMAKWMXQATPR2M.jpg&h=02627874&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■精華展中香港回歸及一國兩制篇幅有所增加。夏家朗攝"},{"pid":"6def338143f5c04d1978109020902ef4566977c8","tid":2442008,"uid":33099,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T05:44:33.000Z","msg":"不如講埋一國兩制偉大構思係由習近平提出"},{"pid":"f1445eef6defa60936b4dd8a07fe60298d4248d9","tid":2442008,"uid":155095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T05:52:16.000Z","msg":"掛中共領導人啲相上去啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/714090/org/d1ad411336e9e9f30ba729f7b72ca266.png/vCa7ZeMAREZXvtBSXP3bP2h0YSZAaHW_aktg02pLYNM?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%